attributionInfo.brokerName: Coldwell Banker Sea Coast Advantage - Washington

data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath brick cottage located in the waterfront town of Washington NC. This beautiful home features natural hardwood floors, a spacious kitchen complete with a chef's dream gas range with double oven, and an enclosed back porch overlooking the fenced in back yard with beautiful mature trees. An unfinished second floor with built in stairs provides the potential for more space. Recent updates to this home include a new roof in 2022 and a new gas pack heating system installed in 2020.  Conveniently located just blocks from beautiful Downtown Washington's waterfront area offering many shopping and dining options, this home is a must see.**An adjacent lot with a large detached garage perfect for storing vehicles or for a workshop is also available for sale.  See MLS #100417127 for that listing.
